.SH "NAME"
lookup_one_len \- filesystem helper to lookup single pathname component
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.HP \w'struct\ dentry\ *\ lookup_one_len('u
.BI "struct dentry * lookup_one_len(const\ char\ *\ " "name" ", struct\ dentry\ *\ " "base" ", int\ " "len" ");"
.SH "ARGUMENTS"
.PP
\fIname\fR
.RS 4
pathname component to lookup
.RE
.PP
\fIbase\fR
.RS 4
base directory to lookup from
.RE
.PP
\fIlen\fR
.RS 4
maximum length
\fIlen\fR
